author: MIT OpenCourseWare
description:
On any given day, MIT Open Learning, MITx, and MIT OpenCourseWare are sharing MIT’s teaching and learning resources with the world—for free. On Thursday, March 13 (https://bit.ly/3QIEb7X), we’ll be raising support to help us meet the needs of learners everywhere, as part of the MIT 24-Hour Challenge. We hope you’ll join us in showing the world the importance of free and open access to knowledge. You and your gift on March 13 will help us meet our giving day goal—and fuel life-changing education.

Twenty, twenty, 24 hours to give…are you up to the challenge?

“I Wanna Be Educated” is a parody of “I Wanna Be Sedated” by The Ramones © 1978 Sire Records, Inc.

Add this to your calendar: https://www.addevent.com/event/nx24537489
